Can't you use a custom matcher function for the sankeyLink? Per [Chevrotian: Custom Token Patterns](https://chevrotain.io/docs/guide/custom_token_patterns.html#usage)
IOW, in `sankeyTokenBuilder.ts` : 
```
case 'SANKEY_LINK_NODE': {
          tokenType.LINE_BREAKS = false;
          tokenType.PATTERN = regexPatternFunc(sankeyLinkNodeRegex);
          break;
``` 
  **tokenType.PATTERN**  can be a function (where you can see if the string matches the a11y title or desc, or overall title  first, and then go on to check to see if it matches the sankey link node.

(I'm playing with that solution now and will post here with whether it works or not.)

